# Development Phases

Signal Deck is built in phases.

Agents should prioritise:

1. MVP shell
2. Rich display
3. History + ECharts
4. Event/scheduled snippets
5. Widgets
6. Debugging toolkit
7. Packaging

See full plan:

ğŸ‘‰ **`docs/design.md`**

