# Behaviour Guidelines for Agents

When contributing:

â€¢ Prefer clarity over cleverness
â€¢ Keep API minimal
â€¢ Add safety checks
â€¢ Make output readable in tables
â€¢ Use monospace formatting
â€¢ Use Nerd Font icons where helpful
â€¢ Do not add backend dependencies unless explicitly requested
â€¢ Do not expand scope into full automation engine

When unsure, optimise for:

ğŸ‘‰ debugging presence logic
ğŸ‘‰ understanding â€œwhy did this happen?â€

These are the primary user needs.

